channel.title: Storm Runner (Feat. Osharu Perez & V-M) - Feedback Wanted!
channel.description:
Wanted to post this new track that I made with the help of @Osharu and @VJM! It would be great to get as much honest feedback on this song as possible. Since being so new to producing, it really helps to get the opinions of others on different things that are good and different things to improve on.
https://soundcloud.com/icymattrix/storm-runner-feat-osharu-perez
